From: Dmitrii Sharshakov <d3dx12.xx@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Feb 2026 15:10:43 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] feat: bootstrap Go in core

Remove Go from the bootstrap path, as it can be independently
bootstrapped from stage1 (+core-filesystem for packaging).

Go is bootstrapped from stage1, because it must be bootstrapped on
i386 or amd64, as arm64 has only been added in Go 1.9.
